People draw people write and collect things, play instruments and so on. nut i cant see one thing that keeps me occupid. Im getting drums soon and was very excited about the fact. Till i relised i mite fail and probile will. It made my feel abit down, then i went and to read what people was saying on old live journal. And saw something that erd said and it made me think, if i just gave up with out even trying what would that make me?

Well the answer is it would make me nothing, i have to try and if i fail so be it. But im going to try and do one thing in my life and make it work, not just for me but for others.
